    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122960/extras/1844ae3e1be0e3e8e098f0607e6eec9c.poster.avif?t=1763045382\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122960/extras/1844ae3e1be0e3e8e098f0607e6eec9c.webm?t=1763045382\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122960/extras/1844ae3e1be0e3e8e098f0607e6eec9c.mp4?t=1763045382\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>岛上的居民过着平静的生活。也许...太平静了...<br><br>直到你出现。你是一只好奇又混乱的海鸥，可以完全自由地飞行、探索和制造些小麻烦。<br><br>你会帮助岛上的居民...还是让他们抓狂？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122960/extras/e253ee5217ff6edc707d93d9b485d4f7.poster.avif?t=1763045382\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122960/extras/e253ee5217ff6edc707d93d9b485d4f7.webm?t=1763045382\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>在充满活力的岛屿上自由飞翔，这里几乎所有东西都可互动<br></li><li>根据心情恶作剧、捉弄或帮助居民<br></li><li>完成有趣的挑战，揭开岛屿的秘密<br></li><li>帮助有需要的动物，并以意想不到的方式与它们相遇<br></li><li>按照地图指引，挖掘宝藏<br></li><li>调查威胁岛屿的奇怪污染并尝试解决问题<br></li><li>享受根据你行为变化的动态音乐<br></li><li>通过你的行动，真正地改变世界<br></li><li>或者只是停在长椅上，静静看着世界流转</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122960/extras/36fed575245aa40344ade8176235926c.poster.avif?t=1763045382\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122960/extras/36fed575245aa40344ade8176235926c.webm?t=1763045382\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>《Goeland》是一款平和又调皮的沙盒冒险游戏，探索、幽默和涌现玩法在此碰撞。<br><br>不喜欢混乱？在《Goeland》中你可以降低紧张度：关闭追逐，放松心情，享受做一只安静小鸟的时光。<br><br>你会成为怎样的一只海鸥？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122960/extras/d3e12bfa4a01723b35dff2084f168b3a.poster.avif?t=1763045382\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122960/extras/d3e12bfa4a01723b35dff2084f168b3a.webm?t=1763045382\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>",
